  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To evaluate the safety and efficacy of an immunosuppressive regimen using synergic action of SRL and CsA, but which will limit (ab initio), the nephrotic effect of such combination. To compare Rapamune/low dose Cyclosporine vs. Rapamune/Steroids.</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
